org.apache.hadoop.hbase.zookeeper

Class ZKMetrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.zookeeper.ZKMetrics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ZKMetricsListener

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class ZKMetrics
extends Object
implements ZKMetricsListener
    Class used to push numbers about ZooKeeper into the metrics subsystem. This will take a single function call and turn it into multiple manipulations of the hadoop metrics system.
